As PB666 has pointed out, electricpants continued from his own post. Rule 2 states that you cannot perform any operation again until another person has successfully perform an operation to change the current number. Vysionne did not made any valid change to the number, thus that post is nulled, and electricpants must wait till another person make a valid post.
